            "duration_seconds": 6.4
          }
        }
      ],
      "flavor_text": "A deathly shroud descends at the border crossing, turning the checkpoint's iron authority into impenetrable shadow. Nothing passes through — not blade, not breath, not the desperate."
    },
    {
