          }
        }
      ],
      "flavor_text": "A smothering wind tears through the checkpoint like something that was never meant to be declared, lifting and scattering whatever stood in its path. The air turns dark and heavy in its wake, the kind of silence that follows a border crossed without permission."
    },
    {
      "id": "skill_000147",
      "name": "Contraband Ignition Volley",
